Cell[TextData[{
 "Form groups of two. However if at this point you had twice the same \
partner, ",
 StyleBox["you need to find a new partner",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 ". \nEach member of the group must understand and be able to explain (in \
detail) all of the code turned in. We allow you to work in groups so that you \
have someone with whom you can talk about your work in detail. This is ",
 StyleBox["not ",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 "meant for group members to only do half of the work. "
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.396480117972228*^9, 3.396480213211784*^9}, {
   3.396481628330934*^9, 3.396481640932308*^9}, {3.397247800613196*^9, 
