Cell[TextData[{
 "c) Write a function",
 StyleBox[" stopRandomWalk3D[lower, upper, start] ",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 "that creates a random walk as in part a). However the length is not set, \
the function  simply stops the walk when the walk (more precisely: the y- or \
z-coordinate) hits either the number in ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   StyleBox["upper",
    FontSlant->"Italic"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "e6c88a29-003b-4a6c-9392-134f5ce788ba"],
 " or the number in ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   StyleBox["lower",
    FontSlant->"Italic"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "06867f8e-99dd-48e3-8dfa-0a3eb4b03cc1"],
 " for the first time. ",
 StyleBox["stopRandomWalk3D[lower, upper, start]",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 " should returns the list of coordinates for the walk and a graph of the \
walk as well  (that is, it returns a list with two items: the plot and the \
list of points (in that order)). Modify this function to create a function ",
 StyleBox["stopPointRandomWalk3D[lower, upper, start] ",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 " that only returns the very last coordinate point of the walk, i.e. a \
single point with coordinates of the form {stop, ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["lower", "y"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "93b0cda4-ba5b-4216-b480-ced6d7cc86e4"],
 " ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["lower", "z"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "2def67cf-b6d8-4e9b-978c-6d541e024cca"],
 "} or {stop, ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    SubscriptBox["upper", "y"], ",", " ", 
    SubscriptBox["upper", "z"]}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "3d52e699-730c-43ae-966c-060463ad785f"],
 "} for some integer stop. "
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.568640235127554*^9, 3.568640624533382*^9}, {
  3.568640706506723*^9, 3.568640856031802*^9}, {3.5686797244692907`*^9, 
  3.5686797357949104`*^9}, {3.5686798375694895`*^9, 3.56867984939431*^9}, {
  3.5686806686545486`*^9, 3.5686806918673897`*^9}, {3.5686810612146387`*^9, 
  3.568681089123088*^9}, {3.568681529449461*^9, 3.568681538060676*^9}, {
  3.5686816441052628`*^9, 3.568681662638095*^9}, {3.568684617422739*^9, 
  3.5686847483799267`*^9}, {3.5686850773272934`*^9, 3.5686850779980946`*^9}, {
  3.7573746705318117`*^9, 3.7573746766283903`*^9}, {3.757374716557313*^9, 
  3.757374740678852*^9}, {3.7583791547978983`*^9, 3.7583792581562333`*^9}, {
  3.7583916647788897`*^9, 
  3.7583917046501703`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"30cfc247-41c8-430a-af1a-\
970f1605468d"],

