Cell["\<\
Think about how you might approach this problem. Then follow the instructions \
below. Also, just like in the last homework, you should write several \
additional functions to simplify and modularize the work. Make sure you add \
good comments prior to each function which explains what its task is.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7584253773119726`*^9, 3.758425451514217*^9}, {
  3.758425593449335*^9, 3.75842560210083*^9}, {3.758499801927089*^9, 
