96414dfd03c2"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[TextData[{
 StyleBox["Locations",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 " in the letterRect are specified by a pair: {row, col} and directions of \
moving from one letter to the next are also specified as a pair {changeInRow, \
changeInCol}. For example when starting in location {3, 2} and moving in \
direction {-1, 1}  leads to locations {3,2}, {2,3}, {1,4}, {0, 5}. The last \
one, of course, is not a valid location. "
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.758399177456313*^9, 3.7583992167445602`*^9}, {
   3.758399254581724*^9, 3.7583992887256775`*^9}, {3.7583994393012896`*^9, 
   3.758399494136426*^9}, {3.758399606483852*^9, 3.7583996104990816`*^9}, {
