Cell["\<\
e) Write a function checkWonder[sq, wordlst] (which calls findAllWords) which \
returns a list containing three lists: a) the list of words from wordlst \
which appear exactly once b) the list of words from wordlst which appear more \
than once c) the list of words from wordlst which do not appear at all.\
